    <h2>About Krenla</h2>
    <p>Krenla is a social platform that combines real-time messaging, community spaces, and discussion threads in a single, privacy-first product. Launched in public beta in 2024, Krenla is home to over 500,000 users and 25,000 communities across technology, gaming, design, science, and education.</p>

    <h2>Key facts</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Founded: 2022, Barcelona</li>
      <li>Users: 500,000+ (public beta)</li>
      <li>Communities: 25,000+</li>
      <li>Funding: $12M Series A</li>
      <li>Team: 18 people across 9 countries</li>
      <li>Business model: Subscription (no advertising)</li>
    </ul>

